{"tid":2067353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"痰尿盅：支共可將港人送中","createTime":"2020-06-17T02:46:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T05:26:14.000Z","uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"60796c6fb936b947bb59f0e25cfdb2dd10ec50bb","tid":2067353,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T02:46:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532526-20200617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532526-20200617.htm&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG%2Fkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=e7209566\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1532526-20200617.htm&h=21d76ef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1532526-20200617.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗表示，港澳辦副主任鄧中華早前的發言反映，絕大部分國家安全的案件由香港特區負責執法及司法工作，遇到極特殊、嚴重的案件，中央會保留管轄權，指出是符合《憲法》及《基本法》，不會削弱香港的司法權。他相信，到極特殊、嚴重的案件將是涉及外交上的事宜，例如有外國勢力干預香港事務，就明顯要由中央處理。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">至於觸犯港區國安法的港人，將來會否要到內地受審，他說，若中央認為有關人士有必要移交內地，亦是一個選項，要視乎中央如何行使管轄權。</span></span>"},{"pid":"0dc06b454494660f03a4ce330c65979917876529","tid":2067353,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T02:46:53.000Z","msg":"好CLS！"},{"pid":"2ce01f9884e7165269fcc51039af805d5156a551","tid":2067353,"uid":74622,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T02:47:51.000Z","msg":"最怕你唔硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974428dff3e5a6e977719f097a0ef7652d119bba","tid":2067353,"uid":63782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T02:50:04.000Z","msg":"點解支那冇引渡條例 有管轄權就可以移交<br />\n但佳仔同樣情況就唔可以移交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9e59f556c5391fd8328e33cfc5aca5fb4265a5","tid":2067353,"uid":335434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T03:13:15.000Z","msg":"港人：支共可將痰尿盅送終<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc86684cd09281ff4b6f00d3ecc90c98ca6e3945","tid":2067353,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:25:34.000Z","msg":"港人可為佢送終"},{"pid":"c4ff909620c9463133065ae872c326c787694be1","tid":2067353,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752c49c90fca75ff024ef678a61b2fd63b8101b8","tid":2067353,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SoiSzK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSoiSzK2.jpg&h=09b464c2&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}